%8a%e8%a8%b4%2c1475%2c20210218%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNHM,109,上訴,1475,20210218,1","JYEAR":"109","JCASE":"上訴","JNO":"1475","JDATE":"20210218","JTITLE":"毒品危害防制條例"}